WEBVTT

00:00.401 --> 00:03.502
Woman: EVERYBODY, REMEMBER,

00:03.504 --> 00:04.603
WE'RE HERE TO HELP
SICK PEOPLE FEEL BETTER.

00:04.605 --> 00:05.704
IT IS NOTHING
TO GET WORKED UP ABOUT.

00:05.706 --> 00:07.106
ON THE DAY YOU'RE SUPPOSED
TO MOVE IN WITH ME?

00:07.108 --> 00:08.974
I KNOW.

00:08.976 --> 00:11.210
- YOU SURE THIS IS
WHAT YOU WANT?
- WE'RE GONNA MAKE THIS WORK.

00:11.212 --> 00:13.545
GUESS NO MATTER
HOW MANY STRIPES YOU
GOT ON THE SLEEVE,

00:13.547 --> 00:15.114
YOU STILL GOTTA KISS
THE RING, HUH, MAJOR?

00:15.116 --> 00:17.483
YES, I DO, OFFICER.

00:17.485 --> 00:19.651
- SO, WHAT'S GOIN' ON?
- POSSIBLE FLU OUTBREAK.

00:19.653 --> 00:21.820
SABINE LOMMERS.
HEALTH AND HUMAN SERVICES.

00:21.822 --> 00:24.623
DR. CANNERTS HAS IDENTIFIED
A POSSIBLE PUBLIC HEALTH THREAT.

00:24.625 --> 00:28.127
Dr. Victor: WITHIN 16 HOURS,
DR. SANDERS BECAME SYMPTOMATIC,

00:28.129 --> 00:32.131
SUGGESTING THAT THE VIRUS
CAN REPLICATE AT
AN ACCELERATED RATE.

00:32.133 --> 00:34.833
WE'RE PLACING YOUR ZONE
OF THE CITY UNDER
COMPLETE QUARANTINE.

00:34.835 --> 00:37.069
ONCE WE'RE 48 HOURS
DISEASE-FREE,

00:37.071 --> 00:38.904
OUR LIVES CAN
GO BACK TO NORMAL.

00:38.906 --> 00:41.006
- I CAN'T LET YOU THROUGH THERE.
- MY GIRL IS IN THERE.

00:41.008 --> 00:42.641
- SO IS MINE.
- GET OUT!

00:42.643 --> 00:44.743
Man: CLEAR!
[PEOPLE SCREAMING]

00:44.745 --> 00:46.578
HOW MUCH LONGER ARE THEY
GONNA EXTEND THE QUARANTINE?

00:46.580 --> 00:47.846
THERE'S SOME THINGS
ABOUT THE CORDON

00:47.848 --> 00:49.214
I'M NOT GONNA BE
ABLE TO TELL YOU.

00:49.216 --> 00:51.216
LEO GREEN,
INTHEPERIMETER.COM.

00:51.218 --> 00:53.218
AND YOU SAY EXACTLY
WHAT THEY WANT YOU TO SAY.

00:53.220 --> 00:55.587
LAST NIGHT I'M A HERO,
BUT TODAY I'M THE ENEMY.

00:55.589 --> 00:57.689
WHERE THERE'S A MOUTHPIECE,
THERE'S A SECRET.

00:57.691 --> 01:00.159
UNTIL THE VIRUS DIES OUT,
WE CAN'T BREAK THE CORDON.

01:00.161 --> 01:03.095
Lex: THEN HOW DO WE GET
THE HEALTHY PEOPLE OUT?

01:03.097 --> 01:04.930
WE DON'T.

01:04.932 --> 01:06.598
[PEOPLE SHOUTING]

01:20.047 --> 01:21.613
[PEOPLE SHOUTING]

01:28.089 --> 01:29.421
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

01:29.423 --> 01:31.056
[PEOPLE YELLING INDISTINCTLY]

01:31.058 --> 01:33.625
Woman: HEY!

01:36.097 --> 01:39.031
A REAL PROBLEM FOR PEOPLE
WHO HAVE FOUND THEMSELVES
TRAPPED IN...

01:39.033 --> 01:41.200
...TERRIFIED AT THIS POINT.
WE HAVE REPORTS OF...

01:41.202 --> 01:42.901
YOU GOT THIS COVERED?

01:42.903 --> 01:45.204
I FEEL LIKE WE'RE
LOCKING THE DOOR ON
A BURNING BUILDING.

01:45.206 --> 01:46.872
PREACHIN' TO THE CHOIR,
WALDEN.

01:46.874 --> 01:49.842
Pete: HOW MANY MORE OF THESE
DO YOU WANT US TO DO?

01:51.645 --> 01:54.213
SEAL THEM ALL.

01:54.215 --> 01:55.714
Woman: ...UNABLE TO
GET TO THEIR PARENTS.

01:55.716 --> 01:58.450
SHOULD BE TERRIFIED
AND MUST BE SO SHAKEN.

01:58.452 --> 02:00.786
Man: AS YOU CAN SEE...

02:02.223 --> 02:03.989
Man: ALL RIGHT, THAT'S IT.

02:05.926 --> 02:09.294
Sabine: THREE DAYS AGO,
WHEN THE CORDON SANITAIRE
WAS ENACTED,

02:09.296 --> 02:12.564
THERE WAS EVERY HOPE
THAT THE VIRUS WOULD BE
CONTAINED QUICKLY.

02:12.566 --> 02:16.301
UNFORTUNATELY, A SMALL NUMBER
OF PEOPLE WERE EXPOSED

02:16.303 --> 02:18.470
WITHIN THE ORIGINAL
48-HOUR WINDOW,

02:18.472 --> 02:20.806
AND WE MADE THE DECISION
TO EXTEND THE QUARANTINE.

02:20.808 --> 02:23.809
Sabine: SHIPPING CONTAINERS
WERE PLACED AROUND THE PERIMETER

02:23.811 --> 02:24.977
TO SECURE THE BORDER.

02:24.979 --> 02:27.079
THE NUMBER OF INFECTED
IS UNDER CONTROL,

02:27.081 --> 02:28.814
AND THE CORDON IS WORKING.

02:28.816 --> 02:30.482
Woman: IF THE CORDON
IS WORKING, DR. LOMMERS,

02:30.484 --> 02:32.284
WHY ADD THE CONTAINERS?

02:32.286 --> 02:34.253
A SECURE CORDON
IS NOT ONLY IMPERATIVE

02:34.255 --> 02:36.855
FOR THIS QUARANTINE TO WORK,
IT'S ALSO HELPFUL FOR OUR POLICE

02:36.857 --> 02:39.091
WHO HAVE THE REST
OF METRO ATLANTA TO COVER.

02:39.093 --> 02:40.626
Man: DR. LOMMERS?

02:40.628 --> 02:43.595
Woman: SINCE THE
ANNOUNCEMENT THAT PATIENT
ZERO IS FROM SYRIA,

02:43.597 --> 02:45.864
THE SYRIAN GOVERNMENT
HAS REPEATEDLY DENIED

02:45.866 --> 02:48.967
HAVING ENGAGED IN
BIOTERRORISM. CAN YOU TELL--

02:48.969 --> 02:50.969
THAT WOULD BE A QUESTION
FOR HOMELAND SECURITY.

02:50.971 --> 02:54.506
Sabine: OUR FOCUS IS TO
CONTAIN THE VIRUS AND TO
GET PEOPLE HOME SAFELY.

02:54.508 --> 02:57.376
WELL, THAT WON'T BE EASY
FOR MUSLIMS IN THE CORDON.

02:57.378 --> 02:59.311
I'M SURE YOU'RE AWARE
OF LEO GREENE'S POST.

02:59.313 --> 03:02.214
Sabine: AS WE WORK TO PROTECT
EVERYONE IN THE CORDON,

03:02.216 --> 03:04.950
MR. GREENE'S FEARMONGERING
IS BOTH IRRESPONSIBLE

03:04.952 --> 03:06.285
AND IMMORAL.

03:06.287 --> 03:09.688
HOW IS POSTING THOSE
INFLAMMATORY IMAGES

03:09.690 --> 03:11.523
ANY DIFFERENT
THAN YELLING "FIRE!"

03:11.525 --> 03:13.292
IN A CROWDED MOVIE THEATER.

03:13.294 --> 03:15.460
THE ACTIONS DEPICTED
IN THAT VIDEO

03:15.462 --> 03:16.962
WERE REPREHENSIBLE.

03:16.964 --> 03:18.530
Woman: WELL, ISN'T IT
A MATTER OF FREE SPEECH?

03:18.532 --> 03:21.466
MISS SAVAGE, SOCIAL MEDIA
CAN BE A TOOL OR A WEAPON.

03:21.468 --> 03:22.568
FOR EVERY ONE
OF THOSE VIDEOS,

03:22.570 --> 03:24.336
I CAN SHOW YOU A HUNDRED
OF PEOPLE COOPERATING.

03:24.338 --> 03:26.138
SO YOU'RE SAYING IT'S SAFE
INSIDE THE CORDON?

03:26.140 --> 03:27.539
MAJOR CARNAHAN.

03:27.541 --> 03:29.341
[CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING]

03:29.343 --> 03:30.909
[PEOPLE MURMURING INDISTINCTLY]

03:30.911 --> 03:33.745
Lex: YES, IF PEOPLE FOLLOW
THE RULES, IT IS.

03:35.182 --> 03:37.516
ZONE 6 IS MY TERRITORY.

03:37.518 --> 03:39.318
I KNOW IT INSIDE AND OUT.

03:39.320 --> 03:40.719
BY AND LARGE,
THESE ARE DECENT PEOPLE,

03:40.721 --> 03:43.088
GOOD NEIGHBORS WHO JUST WANT
TO DO THE RIGHT THING.

03:43.090 --> 03:45.891
Lex: EVERYBODY JUST
NEEDS TO REMAIN CALM.

03:45.893 --> 03:49.194
THE MORE PEOPLE COOPERATE, THE
SOONER THIS WILL ALL BE OVER.

03:49.196 --> 03:50.662
[PEOPLE SHOUTING INDISTINCTLY]

03:52.166 --> 03:53.765
[ELEVATOR BELL DINGS]

03:53.767 --> 03:55.567
Woman on P.A.:
A REMINDER THAT SAFE...

03:55.569 --> 03:57.402
Dr. Victor: SIR,
YOU'RE FACING ME.

03:57.404 --> 03:58.570
NEXT. MICKEY?

03:58.572 --> 04:00.539
REMEMBER THE JACKET?

04:00.541 --> 04:03.208
Dr. Victor: THIS WAY,
PLEASE. THIS WAY, PLEASE.

04:03.210 --> 04:06.211
THIS WAY. PLEASE,
JUST APPROACH.

04:06.213 --> 04:08.146
CAN YOU REMOVE
YOUR MASK?

04:12.453 --> 04:14.920
ALL RIGHT,
THIS WAY, PLEASE.

04:14.922 --> 04:16.421
SON.

04:16.423 --> 04:18.590
Dr. Victor:
YOU TAKE A SEAT.

04:18.592 --> 04:21.226
I DIDN'T WANT TO LEAVE
WITHOUT SAYING "GOOD LUCK."

04:21.228 --> 04:22.427
OH, YOU'LL
BE BACK LATER?

04:22.429 --> 04:24.229
WELL, I--I NEED TO BE
WITH MY WIFE.

04:24.231 --> 04:25.530
SHE'S JUST
A FEW BLOCKS AWAY.

04:25.532 --> 04:27.399
LISTEN, THE ONLY WAY
TO FIND A TREATMENT

04:27.401 --> 04:29.067
OR A VACCINE IS TO
USE THE VIRUS.

04:29.069 --> 04:31.303
AND SINCE IT'S TOO
DANGEROUS TO
TRANSPORT THE VIRUS

04:31.305 --> 04:32.571
OUT OF THE
QUARANTINE ZONE,

04:32.573 --> 04:34.139
I'M THE ONLY DOCTOR
WHO HAS ACCESS TO IT,

04:34.141 --> 04:36.608
AND I CAN'T DO
ANY MORE TESTING
WITHOUT MORE RATS.

04:36.610 --> 04:40.245
PLEASE COME BACK.
I'M COUNTING ON YOU,
BERT.

04:40.247 --> 04:43.482
DOCTOR? TAKE CARE
OF THAT.

04:43.484 --> 04:47.286
OFFICER RILEY,
YOU COME WITH ME.

04:47.288 --> 04:49.454
[BUZZER]

04:49.456 --> 04:51.189
[PEOPLE HACKING AND COUGHING]

04:53.961 --> 04:57.162
Dr. Victor: APOLOGIES FOR
THE GRIM VISUALS.

04:57.164 --> 04:59.698
RUNNING A BIT LOW
ON SPACE.

05:01.001 --> 05:05.170
SOON, WE'LL HAVE NO ROOM
AT THE INN, AS IT WERE.

05:09.243 --> 05:10.842
[FAINTLY]
HELP ME.

05:16.250 --> 05:17.516
WHAT HAPPENS THEN?

05:17.518 --> 05:19.117
WE'RE MOVING THE
NON-INFECTED PATIENTS

05:19.119 --> 05:22.220
TO THE NEAREST
URGENT CARE FACILITY
WITHIN THE CORDON.

05:23.457 --> 05:27.025
AS FOR THE INFECTED,
WELL...

05:27.027 --> 05:29.861
WE'LL DO WHAT WE CAN
TO KEEP THEM COMFORTABLE.

05:35.636 --> 05:37.302
SO, WHAT DO YOU
NEED FROM ME?

05:37.304 --> 05:39.671
HELP WITH TRANSPORT?

05:39.673 --> 05:42.274
I'M AFRAID IT'S
NOT THAT SIMPLE.

05:50.284 --> 05:53.051
THEY'RE NOT A THREAT.

05:53.053 --> 05:55.687
THE VIRUS DIES
A FEW HOURS AFTER THEY DO.

05:55.689 --> 05:57.456
HOW DO YOU KNOW THAT?

05:57.458 --> 06:00.392
'CAUSE THE DOCTORS
WHO MISHANDLED THE
FIRST OF THE DEAD

06:00.394 --> 06:01.693
ARE STILL ALIVE
AND HEALTHY.

06:01.695 --> 06:03.462
IF WE DON'T DEAL
WITH THEIR BODIES,

06:03.464 --> 06:05.797
WE RISK A HOST
OF OTHER DISEASES.

06:05.799 --> 06:07.566
WE DON'T HAVE SUFFICIENT
FACILITIES OR PERSONNEL

06:07.568 --> 06:09.301
HERE TO DEAL WITH
THEM PROPERLY,

06:09.303 --> 06:11.203
SO WE NEED YOUR HELP.

06:11.205 --> 06:13.572
I'M PRETTY SURE
I CAN'T HELP YOU HERE.

06:13.574 --> 06:15.841
I NEED SOMEONE STRONG,

06:15.843 --> 06:19.077
BOTH PHYSICALLY
AND MENTALLY.

06:19.079 --> 06:21.213
WHAT EXACTLY DO YOU
WANT ME TO DO?

06:23.417 --> 06:25.917
THE ONLY THING
WE CAN DO.

06:27.221 --> 06:28.920
BURN THEM.

06:30.491 --> 06:33.558
Dr. Victor: I MUST DECLARE THE
VIRUS AS HIGHLY CONTAGIOUS

06:33.560 --> 06:36.862
AND FATAL IN 100%
OF ITS VICTIMS.

06:36.864 --> 06:39.097
Sabine: I RECOMMEND WE INSTITUTE
A CORDON SANITAIRE

06:39.099 --> 06:41.233
TO CONTAIN THE SPREAD
OF THE VIRUS.

06:41.235 --> 06:42.501
Man: WHAT I NEED IS THE TRUTH.

06:42.503 --> 06:44.336
Man: WE ARE IN THE MIDDLE
OF THE HOT ZONE.

06:44.338 --> 06:45.604
- JANA!
- IF WE LET ANYONE OUT

06:45.606 --> 06:48.306
WE'RE RISKING THE LIVES
OF EVERYONE IN THIS CITY.

06:53.080 --> 06:54.746
[PHONE BEEPS]

06:54.748 --> 06:56.248
Jana: HEY, STRANGER.

06:56.250 --> 06:58.917
Lex: JANA, JANA, I BEEN
WORKING ALL NIGHT.

06:58.919 --> 07:00.685
I WOULD HAVE CALLED YOU EARLIER.
I'M SO SORRY, BABY.

07:00.687 --> 07:01.953
OH, NO. NO "BABY."

07:01.955 --> 07:03.722
WE ARE DEFINITELY
NOT AT "BABY" RIGHT NOW.

07:03.724 --> 07:05.857
- YOU'RE MAD.
- WHY SHOULD I BE MAD?

07:05.859 --> 07:07.926
MY HERO COP BOYFRIEND
IS ALL OVER TV

07:07.928 --> 07:09.694
TELLING PEOPLE THEY'RE
GONNA BE OK,

07:09.696 --> 07:10.896
SO I TELL EVERYONE HERE
TO BELIEVE HIM,

07:10.898 --> 07:12.564
BECAUSE, YOU KNOW,
HE'S ONE OF THE GOOD ONES.

07:12.566 --> 07:14.466
AND THEN I FIND OUT
THROUGH TWITTER

07:14.468 --> 07:16.635
THAT WE'VE ALL BEEN LOCKED IN
BY SHIPPING CONTAINERS.

07:16.637 --> 07:18.904
IT WAS CLASSIFIED.
I COULDN'T TELL YOU.

07:18.906 --> 07:23.341
A HINT. A CODED TEXT.
AN EMOJI.

07:27.548 --> 07:28.647
Lex: YOU HATE EMOJIS.

07:28.649 --> 07:31.383
LITTLE PRISON BAR EMOJI.

07:31.385 --> 07:33.618
I WOULDN'T HAVE HATED THAT.

07:33.620 --> 07:36.054
[SIGHS]

07:36.056 --> 07:37.589
I'M SO SORRY.

07:37.591 --> 07:39.424
I AM SORRY.

07:39.426 --> 07:42.427
YEAH. ME TOO.

07:42.429 --> 07:45.397
- THIS SUCKS.
- YEAH.

07:45.399 --> 07:47.566
HERE'S A TRUTH.

07:47.568 --> 07:49.234
I DON'T KNOW
HOW LONG THIS WILL GO.

07:49.236 --> 07:52.437
SINCE THE VIRUS SPREAD,
IT COULD BE ANYWHERE
INSIDE THE CORDON.

07:52.439 --> 07:53.905
SO YOU NEED TO HUNKER DOWN.

07:53.907 --> 07:55.974
STAY INDOORS.
RATION YOUR FOOD.

07:55.976 --> 07:57.609
WE DON'T HAVE A LOT
OF POLICE IN THERE,

07:57.611 --> 08:00.011
SO I NEED YOU SAFE.

08:00.013 --> 08:02.414
OK?

08:02.416 --> 08:04.082
YOU GOT IT...

08:04.084 --> 08:05.550
MAJOR CARNAHAN.

08:13.494 --> 08:16.828
15 YEARS AGO,
IN THE DARK AGES,

08:16.830 --> 08:19.264
THIS WOULD HAVE BEEN
A LOT EASIER.

08:19.266 --> 08:21.967
IF YOU DON'T WANT
A VIDEO LIKE THAT
GETTING OUT AGAIN,

08:21.969 --> 08:23.768
WE NEED TO GET
MORE COPS INSIDE.

08:23.770 --> 08:25.470
WHAT WE NEED IS TO
SHUT DOWN LEO GREENE.

08:25.472 --> 08:28.006
I'VE SEEN THIS BEFORE
IN EVERY HOT ZONE I'VE BEEN IN.

08:28.008 --> 08:30.642
PEOPLE WANT TO BE GOOD
AND FOLLOW THE RULES
AND THEY DO

08:30.644 --> 08:33.278
UNTIL SOMEONE PUSHES
THE PANIC BUTTON HARD ENOUGH

08:33.280 --> 08:35.547
AND THEY STOP LISTENING
TO THE AUTHORITIES.

08:35.549 --> 08:38.683
WHICH IS EXACTLY WHY
WE NEED MORE COPS INSIDE.

08:38.685 --> 08:40.519
WE CAN'T POLICE
THE INTERNET,

08:40.521 --> 08:41.853
BUT 50 MORE COPS
MAKING SURE THAT--

08:41.855 --> 08:46.024
LEX, THIS ISN'T A PARADE.
THIS IS A QUARANTINE.

08:46.026 --> 08:48.126
NO ONE IN.

08:48.128 --> 08:49.294
NO ONE OUT.

08:49.296 --> 08:53.632
RIGHT NOW, I NEED YOU
TO GO TALK TO LEO GREENE.

08:53.634 --> 08:57.669
OUR BIGGEST ENEMY
IS FEAR...

08:57.671 --> 08:59.571
AND IT'S COMING
FROM HIM.

08:59.573 --> 09:01.273
SHUT HIM DOWN.

09:07.014 --> 09:09.614
- NOT TOO CLOSE!
- CAREFUL, JEN! NO TOUCHING.

09:11.652 --> 09:13.385
IT'S NOT FAIR
THAT THEY GET TO GO.

09:13.387 --> 09:15.387
YOU KNOW IF YOUR MOM
WAS INSIDE THE CORDON,

09:15.389 --> 09:16.588
SHE'D BE HERE, TOO.

09:18.492 --> 09:20.058
HOSPITAL LOCKDOWN
IS OVER, MARY.

09:20.060 --> 09:22.460
WE SHOULD BE HAPPY
OUR FRIENDS GET TO GO HOME.

09:24.031 --> 09:25.497
Boy: WHOO!

09:27.868 --> 09:30.502
HEY, MARY,
YOU WANNA PLAY?

09:36.009 --> 09:38.610
HEY, YOU STILL LOOKING
FOR A PHONE CORD?

09:38.612 --> 09:40.312
NO, THANKS.

09:45.786 --> 09:47.319
ARE YOU OK?

09:51.391 --> 09:54.559
I WAS SUPPOSED TO BRING
SOME SICK SYRIAN KID
TO THE HOSPITAL.

09:54.561 --> 09:57.128
THAT'S IT.
THAT WAS MY JOB.

09:58.899 --> 10:01.533
I HAVE BRAVES TICKETS
THIS WEEKEND.

10:01.535 --> 10:03.768
I JUST WANT TO GO HOME.

10:03.770 --> 10:07.138
YOU KNOW, BARBECUE,
SLEEP IN MY BED.

10:08.475 --> 10:10.508
HOW 'BOUT YOU? YOU OK?

10:12.379 --> 10:14.813
I JUST WANT TO BREATHE.

10:16.483 --> 10:17.983
BUT I CAN'T...

10:17.985 --> 10:20.285
NOT UNTIL THE LAST OF
THEM GETS HOME SAFELY.

10:20.287 --> 10:22.787
HOW MANY GET TO LEAVE THE
HOSPITAL WITH THEIR PARENTS?

10:22.789 --> 10:25.223
NOT ENOUGH.

10:26.793 --> 10:28.960
Woman: THIS IS THE LATEST
FROM INSIDE THE CORDON.

10:28.962 --> 10:30.462
Leo: WHAT DOES THIS MEAN?

10:30.464 --> 10:31.830
Woman: HAZMAT GUY PAINTED ONE

10:31.832 --> 10:33.331
WHERE THE KIDS GOT INFECTED
AT THAT PARTY.

10:33.333 --> 10:37.335
IT CAUGHT ON. IT'S LIKE
THE PLAGUE CROSSES IN EUROPE

10:37.337 --> 10:39.604
OR HOW THEY MARKED
THE HOUSES DURING KATRINA.

10:39.606 --> 10:41.606
[KNOCK ON DOOR]

10:41.608 --> 10:43.208
HOLD ON.

10:45.579 --> 10:47.178
ONE SECOND.

10:48.949 --> 10:50.949
IT'S THE POLICE.
GOTTA GO.

10:50.951 --> 10:54.586
THOSE YOUR CONTACTS
ON THE INSIDE?

10:54.588 --> 10:58.623
UH, THINK I'M GONNA
PLEAD THE 5TH ON THAT ONE.

10:58.625 --> 10:59.858
YOU GONNA ARREST ME?

10:59.860 --> 11:01.326
WHAT, AND MAKE YOU
MORE FAMOUS?

11:01.328 --> 11:04.763
YOU GOTTA STOP
POSTING THOSE VIDEOS.

11:04.765 --> 11:07.132
THERE ARE PEOPLE
AT RISK ON THE INSIDE.

11:07.134 --> 11:09.000
INSTEAD OF ME BEING
ABLE TO DO MY REAL JOB,

11:09.002 --> 11:10.869
I'M HERE TRYING TO
CONVINCE YOU TO STOP

11:10.871 --> 11:13.071
MAKING A BAD SITUATION
WORSE.

11:15.342 --> 11:18.610
YOU REMEMBER THAT STORM
A COUPLE WINTERS BACK?

11:18.612 --> 11:20.011
THE SNOWPOCALYPSE?

11:20.013 --> 11:23.381
EVERY CITY AND STATE OFFICIAL
KNEW THAT STORM WAS COMING,

11:23.383 --> 11:26.818
YET STILL PEOPLE ENDED UP
STRANDED ON THE FREEWAY
FOR 2 DAYS.

11:26.820 --> 11:30.288
NOW, DON'T YOU WONDER
HOW THAT SAME CROWD OF
BUREAUCRATIC IMBECILES

11:30.290 --> 11:31.823
GOT THOSE CONTAINERS
IN PLACE SO FAST?

11:31.825 --> 11:33.892
DO YOU EVER CONSIDER
TRUSTING THE SYSTEM

11:33.894 --> 11:36.528
INSTEAD OF DELIBERATELY
SCARING THE CRAP
OUT OF PEOPLE?

11:36.530 --> 11:40.799
WHAT'S SCARY IS THAT SYSTEM
DELIBERATELY HIDING
THE TRUTH FROM PEOPLE.

11:40.801 --> 11:45.336
MY GUY AT HOMELAND TELLS ME
THERE'S ABSOLUTELY NOTHING
TO THESE BIOTERRORISM CLAIMS.

11:45.338 --> 11:47.972
AND LOMMERS JUST SAID THAT
EXPOSURES ARE UNDER CONTROL,

11:47.974 --> 11:50.408
YET MY FRIENDS ON THE INSIDE
TELL ME DEATH MARKS ON DOORS

11:50.410 --> 11:51.910
ARE CROPPING UP
ALL OVER THE PLACE.

11:51.912 --> 11:53.678
SO WHICH IS IT?
WHAT'S THE REAL STORY?

11:53.680 --> 11:55.380
WHY DON'T YOU TELL ME?

11:55.382 --> 11:56.915
WHATEVER YOU'RE LOOKING
FOR, YOU'RE NOT GONNA
GET IT FROM ME.

11:56.917 --> 11:58.917
I'M NOT TRYING TO
FRIGHTEN PEOPLE,

11:58.919 --> 12:02.020
BUT MAYBE IF I CAN GET
THEM WORKED UP ENOUGH,

12:02.022 --> 12:04.856
THEY'LL STOP BLINDLY
TRUSTING THE SYSTEM
AND START ASKING QUESTIONS.

12:04.858 --> 12:07.225
UNLIKE YOU, APPARENTLY.
UNLIKE MAJOR MOUTHPIECE
HERE IN FRONT OF ME.

12:07.227 --> 12:08.560
WHAT? YOU THINK
I WANNA BE HERE?

12:08.562 --> 12:11.696
I GOT COPS ON THE INSIDE
OUTMANNED 400 TO 1.

12:11.698 --> 12:12.897
YOU THINK I WANNA BE HERE?

12:12.899 --> 12:15.066
400 TO 1, HUH?

12:15.068 --> 12:18.336
IS THAT AN OFFICIAL
COMMENT?

12:18.338 --> 12:19.938
LISTEN TO ME.

12:19.940 --> 12:22.440
I'M GONNA WALK
OUTTA HERE

12:22.442 --> 12:25.577
AND TRY TO DO MY
CIVIC AND MORAL DUTY
TO HELP--

12:25.579 --> 12:27.879
- YOUR MORAL DUTY?
- TO HELP THE PEOPLE
ON THE INSIDE!

12:27.881 --> 12:31.282
- YOU ACTUALLY BELIEVE--
- I EXPECT YOU TO DO THE SAME!

12:31.284 --> 12:33.351
- DO YOU BELIEVE IN THE CORDON?
- I DO.

12:33.353 --> 12:35.453
ALL RIGHT. I HAVE
ONE QUESTION FOR YOU, THEN.

12:35.455 --> 12:38.690
WHAT HAPPENS WHEN SOMEONE
TRIES TO LEAVE THE CORDON?

12:38.692 --> 12:40.725
MAJOR?

12:40.727 --> 12:42.660
YOU SHOOT 'EM?

12:45.866 --> 12:49.667
THAT'S THE DIFFERENCE
BETWEEN ME AND YOU,
MR. GREENE.

12:51.805 --> 12:54.672
YOU'LL NEVER HAVE TO
ANSWER THAT QUESTION.

13:00.313 --> 13:01.579
Lex: DR. LOMMERS.

13:01.581 --> 13:03.815
BEEN THINKING ABOUT A PLAN
TO GET COPS INSIDE.

13:03.817 --> 13:06.251
Leo, on recording:
...OR FAMILIES ARE BEING LEFT...

13:06.253 --> 13:11.122
Sabine: I'M GUESSING LEO
SAID NO.

13:11.124 --> 13:13.758
Leo: THESE ARE NOT IMAGES
YOU WILL SEE ON TELEVISION

13:13.760 --> 13:15.326
OR IN THE MAINSTREAM MEDIA.

13:15.328 --> 13:17.762
[PHONE RINGING]
IT'S NOT HAPPENING
IN SOME FOREIGN COUNTRY.

13:17.764 --> 13:19.397
IT'S HAPPENING HERE.

13:19.399 --> 13:20.632
MR. PRESIDENT.

13:20.634 --> 13:22.133
Leo: THE DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH
AND HUMAN SERVICES

13:22.135 --> 13:23.902
WOULD HAVE YOU BELIEVE
EVERYTHING IS OK

13:23.904 --> 13:25.403
INSIDE THE CORDON.

13:25.405 --> 13:26.504
IT IS NOT.

13:26.506 --> 13:29.407
WITH NO REGARD
FOR THEIR HUMANITY,

13:29.409 --> 13:31.709
YOUR LOVED ONES ARE
BEING SENTENCED TO DEATH.

13:46.026 --> 13:47.759
[CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS]

13:55.635 --> 13:57.168
[CLICK]

14:17.791 --> 14:19.390
[PHONE VIBRATING]

14:22.796 --> 14:24.462
REMEMBER
THAT GUY RIGSBY?

14:24.464 --> 14:26.798
YEAH, PINE STREET
PICKPOCKET.

14:26.800 --> 14:28.733
YEAH. DEAD PICKPOCKET NOW.

14:28.735 --> 14:30.034
WHERE ARE YOU?

14:30.036 --> 14:32.470
Jake: CANNERTS HAS ME
HELPING WITH THE BODIES.

14:32.472 --> 14:34.973
THERE'S A LOT OF DEAD
PEOPLE IN HERE, LEX.

14:34.975 --> 14:37.876
- HOW MANY?
- 12 SO FAR, AT LEAST.

14:37.878 --> 14:41.212
THAT REPORTER, LEO GREENE,
HAS BEEN POSTING SOME PRETTY
INCENDIARY VIDEOS

14:41.214 --> 14:43.047
FROM INSIDE THE CORDON.

14:43.049 --> 14:44.515
PEOPLE ARE BOUND TO HAVE
A REACTION.

14:44.517 --> 14:46.150
DOES THAT MEAN YOU'RE
FINALLY SENDING
MORE COPS IN?

14:46.152 --> 14:48.086
FOR NOW, WE HAVE TO MAKE
DO WITH WHAT WE GOT.

14:48.088 --> 14:50.221
I'LL SET UP A MEET POINT
FOR ALL THE COPS
INSIDE THE CORDON.

14:50.223 --> 14:51.923
ALL RIGHT.
HOW MANY ARE HERE?

14:51.925 --> 14:55.159
INCLUDING YOU? 11.

14:55.161 --> 14:56.861
[SIGHS]

14:56.863 --> 14:58.396
FOR THE WHOLE CORDON?

14:58.398 --> 15:00.064
I WANT YOU TO
RUN POINT ON THIS.

15:00.066 --> 15:03.034
WHAT? NO.
NO, I'M A BEAT GUY.

15:03.036 --> 15:05.603
AND YOU KNOW I LIKE TO
KEEP IT SIMPLE. THERE'S
GOTTA BE SOME STRIPES--

15:05.605 --> 15:08.373
I DON'T NEED STRIPES.
WHAT I NEED IS SOMEONE
I CAN TRUST.

15:08.375 --> 15:12.076
I NEED COPS AT ATMS,
GROCERY STORES,
ANYWHERE PEOPLE GATHER.

15:12.078 --> 15:14.879
THIS IS ALREADY BEEN A DAY
OF ME GETTING THE CRAP
DETAIL, LEX.

15:14.881 --> 15:16.714
THERE HAS TO BE
SOMEONE ELSE.

15:16.716 --> 15:18.249
OFFICER RILEY.

15:19.452 --> 15:21.619
YOU GIVING ME
AN ORDER, MAJOR?

15:21.621 --> 15:23.187
YES, I AM.

15:23.189 --> 15:24.989
DON'T LET ME DOWN.

15:30.363 --> 15:33.398
SERIOUSLY, JANA?
THIS IS HALF OF
WHAT WE HAD YESTERDAY.

15:33.400 --> 15:35.033
WELL, LEX SAID IT
MIGHT TAKE A WHILE.

15:35.035 --> 15:36.434
LEX WHO LIED ABOUT
THE CONTAINERS?

15:36.436 --> 15:38.970
JANA, HE DIDN'T LIE.
HE JUST--WHATEVER.

15:38.972 --> 15:40.204
HE WAS TELLING
THE TRUTH TODAY.

15:40.206 --> 15:41.773
WHAT DID HE SAY...
EXACTLY?

15:41.775 --> 15:43.274
THAT HE DOESN'T
KNOW HOW LONG
THIS WILL LAST

15:43.276 --> 15:44.943
AND WE NEED TO
HUNKER DOWN.

15:44.945 --> 15:46.878
- WE NEED TO MAKE A FOOD RUN.
- HOW IS THAT HUNKERING DOWN?

15:46.880 --> 15:48.446
HAVE YOU EVER
HUNKERED DOWN
WITHOUT FOOD?

15:48.448 --> 15:50.214
THE VIRUS
COULD BE ANYWHERE.

15:50.216 --> 15:51.449
LEX SAID IT'S NOT
SAFE OUT THERE.

15:51.451 --> 15:54.852
LET'S TAKE A VOTE.
ALL IN FAVOR...

15:57.123 --> 15:59.724
SORRY, JANA, BUT
I NEED A VEGETABLE.

15:59.726 --> 16:02.894
Dennis: WE'LL DRAW STRAWS.
LOSER MAKES THE RUN.

16:02.896 --> 16:04.262
WINNER PAYS.

16:04.264 --> 16:06.965
[CASH REGISTER BEEPING]

16:06.967 --> 16:10.234
Teresa: PEOPLE I'VE NEVER
SEEN BEFORE ARE COMING
INTO THE STORE.

16:10.236 --> 16:13.671
Xander: DO YOU REALLY
THINK YOU SHOULD BE
UP ON THAT TABLE?

16:13.673 --> 16:16.574
I MIGHT BE DYING OF THE
PLAGUE, AND YOU'RE
WORRIED ABOUT ME FALLING?

16:16.576 --> 16:18.309
I'M WORRIED ABOUT YOU,
PERIOD.

16:18.311 --> 16:20.812
YOU'RE NOT DYING.
YOU DON'T HAVE
A SINGLE SYMPTOM.

16:20.814 --> 16:23.648
I'VE ONLY BEEN IN
QUARANTINE FOR 20 HOURS,

16:23.650 --> 16:26.317
ALTHOUGH IT FEELS A LOT
LONGER, STUCK IN HERE.

16:26.319 --> 16:28.119
PEOPLE DIE WITHIN 48.

16:28.121 --> 16:31.789
IF YOU WAS SICK,
YOU'D BE HALLUCINATING
OR SOMETHING BY NOW.

16:31.791 --> 16:34.692
DO YOU THINK THAT'S WHAT
THEY'RE GOING THROUGH?

16:34.694 --> 16:36.327
AMY AND EVERYONE?

16:36.329 --> 16:38.997
HAVEN'T HEARD FROM
A SINGLE ONE OF THEM.

16:38.999 --> 16:43.001
ALL MY FRIENDS
OUTSIDE THE CORDON HAVE
BEEN TEXTING LIKE CRAZY.

16:43.003 --> 16:47.271
NOTHING FROM ANY OF THE ONES
WHO WERE AT THAT PARTY.

16:47.273 --> 16:48.606
LISTEN, TERESA.

16:48.608 --> 16:50.508
YOU CAN'T HELP
YOUR FRIENDS,

16:50.510 --> 16:52.677
BUT YOU CAN
HELP YOURSELF.

16:52.679 --> 16:54.345
YOU JUST GOTTA DO
WHATEVER YOU CAN

16:54.347 --> 16:56.347
TO KEEP YOU
AND THE BABY SAFE.

16:56.349 --> 16:59.384
[CASH REGISTER RUNNING]
Woman: 10 BUCKS?

16:59.386 --> 17:01.819
LAST WEEK, THIS WAS 5.

17:01.821 --> 17:03.054
SUPPLY AND DEMAND.

17:03.056 --> 17:04.989
YOU GOTTA BE KIDDING ME.

17:04.991 --> 17:06.791
DO YOU WANT IT OR NOT?

17:11.131 --> 17:13.564
MY MOM IS GOING TO HELL.

17:18.972 --> 17:20.371
WATCH OUT, MOM!

17:20.373 --> 17:21.706
QUENTIN, KNOCK IT OFF!

17:21.708 --> 17:24.142
- HA HA!
- YOU'RE IN TROUBLE.

17:24.144 --> 17:25.910
THEY'RE GOING
STIR CRAZY.

17:27.714 --> 17:30.848
AW, BRITNEY SHOULD BE
RELEASED FROM ISOLATION
ANY MINUTE NOW.

17:30.850 --> 17:33.017
I'M SORRY.
YOU'RE STUCK WITH US.

17:33.019 --> 17:34.685
NOT AS SORRY
AS HER MOM.

17:34.687 --> 17:36.754
SHE'S USED TO DOING
STUFF LIKE THIS WITHOUT
A GUY IN HER LIFE,

17:36.756 --> 17:39.724
AND NOW HERE I AM
4 MONTHS IN PLAYING DAD.

17:39.726 --> 17:42.326
WELL, TAKE IT FROM
ANOTHER SINGLE MOM.

17:42.328 --> 17:44.395
YOU'RE DOING JUST FINE.

17:44.397 --> 17:48.032
HEY, THAT'S IT! ALL OF YOU,
3 CORNERS.

17:48.034 --> 17:50.034
- RIGHT.
- YOU GUYS!

17:50.036 --> 17:51.436
Katie: THEY NEED FRESH AIR.

17:51.438 --> 17:53.771
- 4 TO 6 FEET!
- WELL, WE CAN'T GO OUT.

17:53.773 --> 17:55.273
WE CAN GO...

17:57.444 --> 17:59.744
- AND YOU'RE UP!
- MARY, YOU'RE ON IT.

17:59.746 --> 18:04.415
Thomas: AW, THAT
COMPLETELY HIT THE LINE.

18:04.417 --> 18:06.617
[KIDS TALKING INDISTINCTLY]

18:08.455 --> 18:10.621
Mary: THROW ME THE BALL.

18:26.406 --> 18:29.874
Thomas: MISS KATIE?
I HAVE TO GO.

18:31.144 --> 18:32.443
Mary: THROW IT.

18:32.445 --> 18:34.545
WOULD YOU KEEP AN EYE
ON THEM?

18:34.547 --> 18:37.248
YEAH. PERFECTLY HEALTHY.

18:37.250 --> 18:40.017
HAY FEVER,
JUST LIKE I TOLD HER.

18:41.387 --> 18:44.288
Thomas: I CAN'T WAIT,
MISS KATIE!

18:44.290 --> 18:46.090
THOMAS!

18:46.092 --> 18:47.658
[DOOR OPENS]

18:54.434 --> 18:57.602
GOT LOST.
I CAN'T GET HOME.

18:57.604 --> 18:59.103
THOMAS.

18:59.105 --> 19:00.404
[COUGHING]

19:00.406 --> 19:03.407
Katie: THOMAS, LET'S
TRADE PLACES, OK?

19:03.409 --> 19:07.111
I HAVE TO FIND
MY WAY HOME.

19:07.113 --> 19:09.113
HELP ME FIND MY WAY HOME.

19:09.115 --> 19:10.681
[VOMITING BLOOD]

19:35.842 --> 19:38.709
Bert: I MISS YOUR
COOKING, MICHIE.

19:38.711 --> 19:39.977
[GLASSES CLINK]

19:39.979 --> 19:43.147
WOULDN'T MIND A LITTLE NAP
RIGHT ABOUT NOW.

19:43.149 --> 19:44.882
THAT'S FINE.

19:44.884 --> 19:48.219
AFTER THAT, YOU NEED
TO HEAD BACK TO THE
HOSPITAL

19:48.221 --> 19:50.288
AND DO YOUR JOB.

19:50.290 --> 19:52.223
MY JOB IS
TAKING CARE OF YOU.

19:52.225 --> 19:55.326
WELL, I'M FINE. BUT
THEY SAY ON THE NEWS

19:55.328 --> 19:57.128
THAT THERE ARE MORE
SICK PEOPLE NOW.

19:57.130 --> 19:58.496
THE DOCTOR NEEDS
THOSE RATS.

19:58.498 --> 20:00.965
- I DON'T CARE.
- BUT YOU DO CARE, BERT.

20:00.967 --> 20:03.134
THAT'S ONE OF THE
REASONS I LOVE YOU.

20:19.552 --> 20:22.553
WE CAN'T KNOW FOR SURE
HE WAS EXPOSED.

20:22.555 --> 20:24.488
HE HAD THE MAN'S BLOOD
ON HIS HAND.

20:24.490 --> 20:27.558
NOT ON HIS MOUTH...
EYES.

20:27.560 --> 20:30.194
THERE WAS NO EXPOSURE
TO THE FLUIDS.

20:30.196 --> 20:31.562
DR. CANNERTS...

20:31.564 --> 20:34.131
FALSE OPTIMISM
IS NOT YOUR STRONG SUIT.

20:36.536 --> 20:38.769
THIS WASN'T YOUR FAULT.

20:40.240 --> 20:43.941
IT WAS, ACTUALLY,
BUT THANK YOU.

20:43.943 --> 20:49.513
HIS DAD CALLED ME EARLIER.
HE GOT STUCK AT WORK.

20:49.515 --> 20:51.949
THE ELECTRICAL PLANT
INSIDE THE CORDON
WAS STRESSED TO THE MAX.

20:51.951 --> 20:56.220
AND HE'S THE FOREMAN.
HE...HE ASKED ME TO
LOOK AFTER HIS BOY

20:56.222 --> 20:58.155
WHILE HE FINISHED UP.

21:08.401 --> 21:10.534
Leo, on video:
OUR CO-WORKERS, OUR FRIENDS...

21:10.536 --> 21:12.970
Jana: REX SAID IT WAS
BAD OUT THERE,

21:12.972 --> 21:14.972
BUT I DIDN'T KNOW
HE MEANT THIS BAD.

21:14.974 --> 21:17.208
Leo: THESE ARE NOT IMAGES
YOU WILL SEE ON TELEVISION.

21:17.210 --> 21:18.709
SORRY I VOTED
AGAINST YOU.

21:18.711 --> 21:21.479
LET'S BE HONEST, SOOZ.
YOU WEREN'T VOTING
AGAINST ME.

21:21.481 --> 21:23.381
YOU WERE VOTING
WITH DENNIS.

21:23.383 --> 21:25.616
Leo: ...DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH
AND HUMAN SERVICES...
[ELEVATOR DINGS]

21:25.618 --> 21:27.885
THE MEN HAVE
RETURNED FROM WAR.

21:36.596 --> 21:39.163
LET THE SHOW
OF GRATITUDE BEGIN.

21:40.433 --> 21:42.967
- WAIT. DON'T.
- WHAT?

21:42.969 --> 21:45.069
YOUR GLOVES.
YOU'RE NOT WEARING GLOVES.

21:45.071 --> 21:48.439
- WELL, I--I JUST TOOK THEM OFF.
- WHEN?

21:48.441 --> 21:49.940
UH...I DON'T KNOW.
ON THE WAY BACK?

21:49.942 --> 21:51.509
TONY, DID YOU SEE
WHERE DENNIS TOOK THEM OFF?

21:51.511 --> 21:53.411
I DIDN'T NOTICE.

21:53.413 --> 21:56.414
I THINK HE HAD 'EM
ON AT THE STORE.

21:56.416 --> 21:58.349
I THINK YOU SHOULD
STAY IN QUARANTINE.

21:58.351 --> 22:00.951
- TO BE SAFE.
- QUIT SCREWIN' AROUND, JANA.

22:00.953 --> 22:02.753
YOU MAY HAVE BEEN EXPOSED.
YOU'VE BEEN OUTSIDE.

22:02.755 --> 22:04.655
BECAUSE WE WENT
TO GET YOU FOOD!

22:04.657 --> 22:07.958
NOW--SUZY, I--I
SANITIZED MY HANDS, OK?

22:07.960 --> 22:09.527
JANA, THEY ONLY WENT
TO THE STORE.

22:09.529 --> 22:11.295
OK, LOOK, WE'VE ALL
SEEN THE NEWS.

22:11.297 --> 22:13.431
IT'S JUST 48 HOURS.

22:13.433 --> 22:17.101
JANA, IF YOU WANT
ANY OF THIS FOOD,

22:17.103 --> 22:18.369
YOU LET US IN RIGHT NOW.

22:18.371 --> 22:21.472
I'M SORRY. I DON'T
LIKE IT EITHER.

22:21.474 --> 22:24.241
FINE. LET'S TAKE A VOTE.

22:29.482 --> 22:33.317
SUZY, YOUR VOTE
MAKES 3!

22:33.319 --> 22:34.885
[POUNDING ON GLASS]
SUZY!

22:34.887 --> 22:37.722
BUZZ US IN NOW!

22:37.724 --> 22:41.392
HAPPY?

22:41.394 --> 22:42.960
[POUNDING ON GLASS]
SUZY!

22:42.962 --> 22:44.628
SUZY!

22:44.630 --> 22:46.263
Dennis: SUZY...

22:51.304 --> 22:52.903
[GRUNTING]

22:54.741 --> 22:56.674
Leo: PEOPLE ARE SCARED,
THEY PAY ATTENTION.

22:56.676 --> 22:58.175
I'D LOVE TO DROP
THE NEXT VIDEO

22:58.177 --> 23:00.077
WHILE THEY'RE STILL
TALKING ABOUT THE LAST ONE.

23:00.079 --> 23:02.146
Melinda: WE'RE GONNA
CHECK OUT THE EDGE
OF THE CORDON NEXT.

23:02.148 --> 23:04.548
YOU GUYS ARE BAD-ASS.
IT'S LIKE THE OLD DAYS, MEL.

23:04.550 --> 23:06.050
EXCEPT YOU'RE NOT
HITTING ON ME.

23:06.052 --> 23:08.219
WHEN THIS THING IS OVER,
YOU GUYS CAN WRITE
YOUR OWN TICKET.

23:08.221 --> 23:10.654
THAT'LL BE US,
LIVIN' THE DREAM.

23:10.656 --> 23:13.924
Leo: ALL RIGHT,
GET BACK OUT THERE.
GOTTA FEED THE BEAST.

23:16.696 --> 23:19.096
Teresa: I HAD TO DO SOMETHING
TO TAKE MY MIND OFF THINGS,

23:19.098 --> 23:23.567
SO HAPPY VALENTINE'S DAY...
SUPER LATE.

23:23.569 --> 23:25.669
I USED FLOUR AND WATER
FOR GLUE.

23:25.671 --> 23:27.505
IS IT FOOD? IS IT ART?

23:27.507 --> 23:29.106
[BOTH GIGGLE]

23:29.108 --> 23:31.842
I COULD DO LIKE A WHOLE SHOW
FROM THIS PLACE.

23:31.844 --> 23:33.544
I'LL BET YOU COULD.

23:33.546 --> 23:37.014
HAPPY SUPER-LATE
VALENTINES DAY
TO YOU, TOO, T.

23:37.016 --> 23:38.482
[SCREECH]

23:44.557 --> 23:48.893
Xander: YOU KNOW, I WISH
YOU WOULDN'T DO THAT.

23:48.895 --> 23:51.395
OK, THAT'S NOT GOOD.

23:51.397 --> 23:52.563
THAT'S HER, HARLEY.

23:52.565 --> 23:55.599
[RIFLE COCKS]
Woman: OHH! AAH!

23:55.601 --> 23:59.136
Harley: STORE'S CLOSED,
EVERYBODY! GO HOME!

23:59.138 --> 24:00.704
[PEOPLE SCREAMING]
WAIT, WAIT. YOU CAN'T JUST--

24:00.706 --> 24:02.807
[GUNSHOT]
WHAT THE HELL WAS THAT?

24:02.809 --> 24:05.476
I GOTTA CALL YOU BACK.

24:05.478 --> 24:07.111
TAKE ALL YOU WANT,
JOZELLE.

24:12.919 --> 24:15.886
Operator: IF YOU'RE CALLING
FROM INSIDE THE CORDON,

24:15.888 --> 24:17.421
PRESS 1.

24:17.423 --> 24:18.789
[RINGING]

24:18.791 --> 24:21.158
WE'RE SORRY.
ALL CIRCUITS ARE BUSY.

24:21.160 --> 24:23.360
PLEASE HANG UP
AND TRY AGAIN LATER.

24:30.403 --> 24:31.802
Harley: COME ON, GIRL.
HURRY UP.

24:31.804 --> 24:34.438
[PHONE VIBRATING]
Harley: TAKE IT ALL.

24:34.440 --> 24:35.773
WHAT THE HELL HAPPENED?

24:35.775 --> 24:38.442
WE'RE BEING ROBBED,
AND THERE'S NO 911.

24:38.444 --> 24:40.444
JUST STAY WHERE
YOU ARE, TERESA.

24:40.446 --> 24:41.846
I GOTTA HELP MY MOM.

24:41.848 --> 24:44.181
T, I SWEAR TO GOD,
I WILL PARACHUTE
INTO THE CORDON

24:44.183 --> 24:45.950
IF YOU DON'T
STAY IN THAT ROOM.

24:45.952 --> 24:47.451
I CAN'T JUST DO NOTHING.

24:47.453 --> 24:48.652
TERESA!

24:48.654 --> 24:50.387
HELLO, HARLEY.

24:53.793 --> 24:56.460
Jake: BAKER,
WE DON'T NEED THAT.

24:56.462 --> 24:58.295
THESE BOYS
ARE JUST LEAVING.

24:58.297 --> 25:00.631
LOOKS LIKE 3 TO 2
TO ME.

25:00.633 --> 25:04.034
YOUR FACE IS ON
VIDEO SURVEILLANCE.

25:04.036 --> 25:06.837
RIGHT NOW, I GOT YOU
FOR EXPIRED PLATES.

25:06.839 --> 25:12.176
IF YOU DROP THE
STUFF AND GO, WE CAN
LEAVE IT AT THAT.

25:12.178 --> 25:14.478
BE A SHAME FOR YOU
TO GO TO PRISON FOR
20 YEARS

25:14.480 --> 25:16.847
JUST FOR SOME
GROCERIES.

25:22.455 --> 25:24.054
COME ON.

25:29.662 --> 25:31.795
GET THE DOOR.

25:31.797 --> 25:33.430
Jake: BAKER.

25:35.334 --> 25:36.800
LET'S GO, HONEY.

25:36.802 --> 25:39.303
WATCH THAT DOOR
AND CHECK THIS ROOM.

25:45.578 --> 25:49.880
ARE YOU KIDDING ME?
THIS VIDEO SURVEILLANCE
ISN'T EVEN HOOKED UP.

25:49.882 --> 25:51.815
HEY, DOES IT MATTER?
HE BOUGHT IT.

25:51.817 --> 25:54.385
[CAR DOORS SLAM;
ENGINE STARTS]

26:00.226 --> 26:03.727
ARE YOU CRAZY?
WHAT IF THEY NOTICED
THAT CORD WAS UNPLUGGED?

26:03.729 --> 26:06.530
YOU CAN AFFORD TO
PLAY GAMES, JAKE.
YOU'RE WEARING A VEST.

26:06.532 --> 26:08.265
YOU THINK THIS IS
A GAME, BAKER?

26:08.267 --> 26:10.734
YOU THINK I LIKE BEING
OUTGUNNED AND OUTNUMBERED
IN HERE?

26:10.736 --> 26:12.903
THIS VEST DOESN'T GET ME
ANYWHERE IF ENOUGH PEOPLE
ARE SHOOTING, OK?

26:12.905 --> 26:15.272
THE WHOLE POINT IS TO
KEEP THEM FROM FIRING.

26:15.274 --> 26:20.511
I'M A COP, JAKE.
I DIDN'T SIGN UP
FOR A SUICIDE MISSION.

26:25.117 --> 26:26.483
[BEEP]

27:01.454 --> 27:03.821
Sabine: CONGRESS WOULD
NEVER LET THIS SLIDE.

27:03.823 --> 27:05.889
THE ACLU IS GONNA JUMP
ALL OVER ME.

27:05.891 --> 27:08.525
- DR. LOMMERS.
- EXCUSE ME.

27:11.297 --> 27:14.598
I KNOW HOW WE CAN GET
MORE COPS IN THERE.

27:14.600 --> 27:15.966
WE USE THE CONTAINER
AS A SLUICE,

27:15.968 --> 27:17.801
A PASSAGEWAY IN AND OUT.

27:17.803 --> 27:19.336
EACH COP THAT EXITS

27:19.338 --> 27:20.904
WILL BE QUARANTINED FOR
48 HOURS INSIDE THE SLUICE

27:20.906 --> 27:22.406
UNTIL WE KNOW THAT
THEY'RE HEALTHY.

27:22.408 --> 27:24.108
SO YOU'RE PITCHING
A ONE-AT-A-TIME PLAN?

27:24.110 --> 27:26.744
IT'S PRECISE EXTRACTION.
I KNOW IT SOUNDS COMPLICATED--

27:26.746 --> 27:29.346
BUT WHAT ABOUT THE
OFFICERS THAT YOU'RE
SENDING IN THERE?

27:29.348 --> 27:31.482
DO ANY OF THEM HAVE
LOVED ONES INSIDE

27:31.484 --> 27:33.617
THAT WOULD MAKE PUTTING
THEIR LIVES ON
THE LINE WORTH IT,

27:33.619 --> 27:35.252
OR IS THAT JUST YOU?

27:35.254 --> 27:38.322
WE'RE POLICE. WE PUT
OUR LIVES ON THE LINE
EVERY DAY.

27:38.324 --> 27:40.357
TRUE, ALTHOUGH I WONDER
IF YOU TOOK A POLL

27:40.359 --> 27:43.961
ASKING WHO VOLUNTEERS
TO WILLINGLY ENTER
THE HOT ZONE

27:43.963 --> 27:46.630
JUST HOW MANY
EAGER COPS YOU'D FIND.

27:46.632 --> 27:48.032
FOLLOWING ORDERS
IS OUR JOB.

27:48.034 --> 27:50.668
GOOD. THEN I'D LIKE
YOU TO DROP THIS
ENTIRE MISSION.

27:50.670 --> 27:54.304
I GOT 11 COPS IN THERE
MANAGING 4,000
TERRIFIED PEOPLE

27:54.306 --> 27:55.873
WHO THINK THAT THEY'VE
BEEN SENTENCED TO DEATH.

27:55.875 --> 27:58.008
THEY HAVE BEEN SENTENCED
TO DEATH, MAJOR,

27:58.010 --> 28:00.210
IF THEY DON'T
FOLLOW THE RULES.

28:00.212 --> 28:02.513
THE RULES WILL
KEEP THEM SAFE.

28:02.515 --> 28:04.381
AND IF WE ADD MORE
BODIES INTO THAT MIX,

28:04.383 --> 28:06.383
EVEN POLICE BODIES,
WE ARE STATISTICALLY

28:06.385 --> 28:10.054
COMPROMISING THE PEOPLE
INSIDE'S ABILITY TO
REMAIN HEALTHY.

28:10.056 --> 28:12.790
I HAVE FEDERAL JURISDICTION.

28:12.792 --> 28:14.591
SO I GUESS
THAT'S AN ORDER.

28:15.895 --> 28:17.628
YES, MA'AM.

28:21.634 --> 28:23.600
Sabine: WHERE WERE WE?

28:25.404 --> 28:26.904
[SLAM]

28:28.641 --> 28:30.240
[MAN COUGHS]

28:36.515 --> 28:39.316
THOMAS? DR. CANNERTS?

28:39.318 --> 28:41.618
DR. CANNERTS!

28:44.256 --> 28:46.390
MR. GRAHAM.

28:46.392 --> 28:48.025
I'VE COME TO TAKE
MY SON HOME.

28:48.027 --> 28:50.060
BUT HE'S BEEN EXPOSED.
YOU CAN'T.

28:50.062 --> 28:52.129
I SAID I'VE COME
TO TAKE HIM HOME.

28:52.998 --> 28:56.100
MR. GRAHAM,
IF THOMAS IS SICK...

28:56.102 --> 29:00.070
DR. CANNERTS,
CALL 911, JAKE, ANYONE.

29:00.072 --> 29:01.839
Dr. Victor:
I ALREADY TRIED, KATIE.

29:01.841 --> 29:06.243
MR. GRAHAM, PLEASE.

29:06.245 --> 29:07.845
LET HIM STAY HERE
SO WE CAN KEEP AN EYE ON HIM.

29:07.847 --> 29:11.682
- YOU MAY BE RISKING--
- YOU WERE SUPPOSED TO
TAKE CARE OF HIM!

29:11.684 --> 29:13.117
YOU!

29:16.789 --> 29:19.857
[RATS SQUEAKING]
KATIE?

29:19.859 --> 29:24.628
SIR, YOU KNOW IT'S
NOT RIGHT TO WAVE A
GUN IN A LADY'S FACE.

29:31.637 --> 29:33.670
I DON'T WANT TROUBLE.

29:34.940 --> 29:38.675
I JUST WANT TO TAKE
MY SON HOME.

29:42.548 --> 29:46.283
Bert: WELL, THOMAS,
LOOKS LIKE YOU'LL BE
GOING HOME TODAY.

29:47.753 --> 29:50.988
AND SOON, WITH THESE
RATS, THE DOCTOR AND I
WILL FIND A WAY

29:50.990 --> 29:53.991
TO FIX EVERYBODY
RIGHT UP. OK?

29:53.993 --> 29:55.826
OK, MR. BERT.

29:55.828 --> 29:58.328
Thomas: BYE, MISS KATIE.

30:05.838 --> 30:08.338
[BREATHING HARD]

30:14.747 --> 30:16.146
I DON'T SEE IT.

30:16.148 --> 30:17.848
Allie: BIGGEST NEWS YET.

30:17.850 --> 30:20.517
IT'S A FIRE ESCAPE.
SO WHAT?

30:20.519 --> 30:22.186
THE WINDOWS ARE SEALED
FROM OUTSIDE.

30:22.188 --> 30:23.821
YOU'RE STILL
MISSING IT.

30:27.493 --> 30:29.159
IT'S A LADDER MOUNT
ON THE ROOF.

30:29.161 --> 30:31.662
Melinda:
ONE SMART PERSON MAKES
IT TO THAT ROOFTOP,

30:31.664 --> 30:34.264
IT'S AN EASY LEAP FROM
THAT FIRE ESCAPE TO THE
TOP OF THE CONTAINER.

30:34.266 --> 30:35.999
THERE'S A WAY TO
GET OUT OF THE CORDON.

30:36.001 --> 30:39.036
TILL THEY FIGURE IT OUT
AND TEAR DOWN THAT FIRE ESCAPE.

30:41.106 --> 30:42.372
I DON'T KNOW.

30:42.374 --> 30:44.708
DON'T GO GETTING
SQUEAMISH, LEO.

30:44.710 --> 30:46.009
WHAT DID WE SAY
IN COLLEGE?

30:46.011 --> 30:47.845
WHEN WE WERE SMOKING HASH?

30:47.847 --> 30:50.380
ALWAYS GIVE PEOPLE
THE REAL STORY.

30:50.382 --> 30:52.549
LEO, THE FACT THAT
LOMMERS IS TRYING TO
SHUT YOU DOWN

30:52.551 --> 30:54.218
MEANS YOU'RE DOING
SOMETHING RIGHT.

30:54.220 --> 30:56.220
THEY LIED ABOUT IT
BEING BIOTERRORISM,

30:56.222 --> 30:57.988
THEY LIED ABOUT
THE NUMBER OF BODIES,

30:57.990 --> 31:00.357
THEY SURE AS HELL
ARE LYING WHEN THEY SAY
EVERYTHING'S OK IN HERE!

31:00.359 --> 31:02.125
YOU DON'T HAVE TO EXPOSE
THE LOCATION.

31:02.127 --> 31:03.994
THE MINUTE YOU POST
THAT IT EXISTS,

31:03.996 --> 31:06.129
COPS WILL FIND IT,
THEY'LL SEAL IT UP,

31:06.131 --> 31:07.898
BUT AT LEAST THE PEOPLE
ARE GONNA KNOW THE WHOLE STORY.

31:07.900 --> 31:11.702
Allie: COME ON, LEO. ISN'T
THAT WHAT WE'RE DOING HERE?

31:13.539 --> 31:16.039
I COULD MAKE OUT WITH
YOU BOTH RIGHT NOW.

31:16.041 --> 31:17.541
YOU GOTTA GET OUT OF THERE.

31:17.543 --> 31:19.042
MAKE A RUN FOR IT
WHILE YOU STILL CAN.

31:19.044 --> 31:20.544
Melinda:
ARE YOU KIDDING?

31:20.546 --> 31:22.846
THIS IS THE HOTTEST
STORY IN THE W--

31:22.848 --> 31:25.749
[COUGHING]

31:25.751 --> 31:27.784
IT'S THE HOTTEST
STORY IN THE WORLD.

31:38.097 --> 31:39.897
[SIRENS IN DISTANCE]

31:46.405 --> 31:47.804
[METAL CLANGING]

31:56.582 --> 31:59.249
WHAT, THEY RUN OUT
OF RAZORS ALREADY?

31:59.251 --> 32:01.451
THIS IS REGULATION
IN THE CORDON NOW.

32:01.453 --> 32:04.187
WHAT? YOU'RE THE ONE
WHO PUT ME IN CHARGE.

32:06.225 --> 32:08.091
WHAT'S IN THESE?

32:08.093 --> 32:11.628
GUNS, AMMO,
GLOVES, GEAR.

32:11.630 --> 32:14.531
YES, YES. THAT'S WHAT
I'M TALKIN' ABOUT.

32:14.533 --> 32:17.501
ALL RIGHT, SO WHERE'S
MY REINFORCEMENTS?

32:21.907 --> 32:24.107
YOU'RE KIDDING ME, RIGHT?

32:24.109 --> 32:27.077
DO YOU KNOW WHO YOU
GAVE ME IN HERE?

32:27.079 --> 32:30.647
A SERGEANT WHO TOOK A WALK
WHEN HE SAW I DIDN'T HAVE
ANY STRIPES,

32:30.649 --> 32:32.983
A NARCO I'M PRETTY SURE
WAS HOPPED UP,

32:32.985 --> 32:35.619
A BUNCH OF ROOKIES,
AND A TRAFFIC COP.

32:35.621 --> 32:37.988
I ALREADY LOST 2
WHEN THEY SAW THE ODDS,

32:37.990 --> 32:39.656
AND THE REST AREN'T EXACTLY
THE A-TEAM IN HERE.

32:39.658 --> 32:41.959
I KNOW I'M ASKING
THE IMPOSSIBLE.

32:41.961 --> 32:43.961
NO, NO. YOU GOT
THE WRONG GUY.

32:45.431 --> 32:48.165
YOU'D HAVE FOUND A WAY
TO KEEP THOSE GUYS
FROM WALKING.

32:48.167 --> 32:50.500
THIS IS DEAD HERO
TERRITORY, MAN.
IT'S NOT MY THING.

32:50.502 --> 32:53.670
AND NEITHER WAS
GOING TO CLASS OR
STAYING OUT OF TROUBLE.

32:53.672 --> 32:56.873
I WASN'T EASIER
ON YOU THEN EITHER!

32:59.445 --> 33:03.413
IT KIND OF WORKED OUT
FOR THE BOTH OF US,
WOULDN'T YOU SAY?

33:08.821 --> 33:10.887
[CHUCKLING]

33:12.925 --> 33:14.524
[PHONE DINGS]

33:18.797 --> 33:20.597
WHAT?

33:20.599 --> 33:23.266
LEO GREENE JUST TOLD
THE WHOLE DAMN WORLD

33:23.268 --> 33:25.602
THERE'S A WAY
TO ESCAPE THE CORDON.

33:33.312 --> 33:35.045
[PHONE BEEPING]
Lex: DR. LOMMERS.

33:35.047 --> 33:36.546
WE'RE HEADIN'
OUT THERE NOW.

33:36.548 --> 33:38.849
AN OFFICER INSIDE
THE CORDON LOCATED
THE BREACH.

33:38.851 --> 33:40.884
GOOD. I JUST GOT WORD
FROM THE GOVERNOR.

33:40.886 --> 33:43.153
AS YOU SECURE THE AREA,
YOU ARE EMPOWERED

33:43.155 --> 33:45.222
TO DEFEND THE CORDON
WITH DEADLY FORCE.

33:45.224 --> 33:47.357
GOOD LUCK, LEX.

33:47.359 --> 33:50.360
- ALL RIGHT, SIT UP.
- EYES OPEN.

33:50.362 --> 33:52.129
OK, LISTEN. OUR JOB
IS SIMPLE.

33:52.131 --> 33:54.364
THE FIRE DEPARTMENT
OUTSIDE IS GONNA TAKE
DOWN THE FIRE ESCAPE

33:54.366 --> 33:56.066
NEAR THE CONTAINERS.

33:56.068 --> 33:59.736
WE JUST HAVE TO MAKE SURE
NO ONE GETS UP THERE
BEFORE THEY'RE DONE.

33:59.738 --> 34:01.405
- YOU SEE 'EM?
- LET'S GO.

34:01.407 --> 34:03.974
- GET SOME ON OUR WAY.
- NOW, KEEP YOUR VISORS DOWN.

34:03.976 --> 34:06.243
Man: YEAH.
RIGHT AROUND THERE.

34:06.245 --> 34:08.011
- FAN OUT!
- ALL RIGHT, SPREAD OUT.

34:08.013 --> 34:09.980
Man: FAN AS YOU GET UP TO...

34:09.982 --> 34:11.748
HOW THE HELL
DID WE MISS THIS?

34:11.750 --> 34:13.383
- SET 'EM UP ON THE TOP.
- OK.

34:13.385 --> 34:14.751
Man: HEY, WHAT'S GOIN' ON?

34:14.753 --> 34:16.520
- BAKER, HOLD 'EM BACK.
- COME ON.

34:16.522 --> 34:19.322
[MAN COUGHING]
Woman: OR YOU CAN GO, RAY.

34:19.324 --> 34:21.725
IF ANYBODY TRIES
TO BREACH THE CORDON,

34:21.727 --> 34:26.196
YOUR ORDERS ARE TO STOP THEM
BY ANY MEANS NECESSARY.

34:26.198 --> 34:29.032
[SHOUTING]
Man: GET BACK! GET BACK!

34:29.034 --> 34:30.400
[PHONE BEEPS]

34:30.402 --> 34:32.169
- WHAT THE HELL'S
HAPPENING OVER THERE?
- YEAH.

34:32.171 --> 34:33.770
Jake:
HOW MUCH LONGER?

34:33.772 --> 34:36.673
- ALMOST THERE.
- WE'RE CLOSE.

34:36.675 --> 34:39.042
WHAT'S HAPPENING IN THERE?

34:39.044 --> 34:40.677
[SHOUTING]

34:40.679 --> 34:42.045
CROWD THICKENS.

34:42.047 --> 34:43.447
THINK YOU CAN HOLD THEM?

34:43.449 --> 34:46.716
[CRASH] YEAH, AS LONG AS
THEY JUST WANT TARGET
PRACTICE.

34:46.718 --> 34:49.119
- YOU CAN'T MAKE ME GO--
- BREAK IT UP!

34:49.121 --> 34:51.054
[SHOUTING GETTING LOUDER]

34:51.056 --> 34:54.691
Woman: RUN! RUN!

34:54.693 --> 34:56.059
FULL SUPPORT!

34:56.061 --> 34:57.627
Man: UGH!

34:57.629 --> 34:59.896
AH, DON'T TOUCH HIM!
DON'T TOUCH HIM!
DON'T TOUCH HIM!

34:59.898 --> 35:01.131
Woman: PIG!

35:01.133 --> 35:02.699
Woman: GO!

35:02.701 --> 35:04.201
Man: GO, GO, GO!

35:04.203 --> 35:05.969
FOLLOW THEM!

35:05.971 --> 35:08.405
HEY, LEX. LEX.

35:08.407 --> 35:10.107
HEY, BAKER, WITH ME.

35:15.047 --> 35:16.446
[GUNS COCK]

35:16.448 --> 35:18.548
[LADDER RATTLES AND FALLS]

35:18.550 --> 35:19.816
DAMN IT.

35:19.818 --> 35:22.319
Lex: SIR, YOU ARE
BREAKING THE LAW.

35:22.321 --> 35:24.221
TURN BACK NOW.

35:33.065 --> 35:34.631
I NEED YOU TO STEP AWAY.

35:34.633 --> 35:37.334
SIR, THIS IS YOUR
FINAL WARNING!

35:37.336 --> 35:39.736
STEP AWAY FROM THE EDGE,
OR WE WILL SHOOT.

35:39.738 --> 35:41.838
IS HE SICK?
I--I CAN'T TELL.

35:41.840 --> 35:43.340
DOESN'T MATTER.

35:43.342 --> 35:45.675
NO ONE IN, NO ONE OUT.
THOSE ARE THE RULES.

35:45.677 --> 35:47.310
[INHALES]

35:47.312 --> 35:49.679
[COCKS GUN]

35:49.681 --> 35:51.648
SIR, THIS IS YOUR
FINAL WARNING!

35:51.650 --> 35:56.052
STEP AWAY FROM THE EDGE
OR WE WILL SHOOT!

35:57.956 --> 36:01.291
[NUMEROUS GUNSHOTS]

36:01.293 --> 36:03.059
Man: OHH!

36:04.463 --> 36:06.696
[PEOPLE TALKING INDISTINCTLY]

36:12.137 --> 36:13.737
MY WIFE AND KIDS
ARE OUT THERE.

36:16.108 --> 36:18.208
IF HE WAS SICK...

36:22.981 --> 36:25.215
BAKER...

36:25.217 --> 36:27.717
I'M DONE.

36:53.512 --> 36:55.745
[BODY BAG SCRAPING FLOOR]

37:27.446 --> 37:30.180
KATIE, HEY.

37:30.182 --> 37:35.218
CANNERTS TOLD ME
WHAT HAPPENED.

37:35.220 --> 37:36.953
I'M SORRY.

37:36.955 --> 37:39.923
WHAT ARE YOU EVEN
DOING DOWN HERE?

37:39.925 --> 37:43.260
TURNS OUT I'M WORKIN'
2 JOBS THESE DAYS.

37:45.297 --> 37:47.464
THESE ARE PEOPLE WHO...

37:49.067 --> 37:53.603
FIGURE SOMEONE SHOULD
REMEMBER THEM WITH
SOME RESPECT.

37:55.574 --> 37:58.241
LISTEN,
I KNOW IT'S ROUGH.

37:58.243 --> 38:01.544
OK? BUT THESE PEOPLE IN
HERE, THEY DIED ALONE.

38:01.546 --> 38:04.614
AT LEAST THOMAS GETS
TO BE WITH HIS FAMILY.

38:04.616 --> 38:06.483
AND WHAT IF IT
WERE QUENTIN?

38:06.485 --> 38:09.986
HE'D WANT TO BE WITH YOU.

38:09.988 --> 38:12.922
I JUST--I DON'T KNOW HOW
THIS WORLD WORKS IN HERE.

38:12.924 --> 38:16.126
I MEAN, A MAN WITH A GUN
WALKED IN HERE AND STOLE
HIS KID,

38:16.128 --> 38:18.561
AND NOBODY COULD DO
ANYTHING TO STOP HIM.

38:18.563 --> 38:22.265
IF IT'S LIKE THAT IN HERE,
WHAT IS IT LIKE OUTSIDE
THE WALLS OF THIS HOSPITAL?

38:22.267 --> 38:23.733
I MEAN, WHO'S IN CHARGE?

38:27.506 --> 38:29.306
LOOKS LIKE I AM.

38:32.844 --> 38:34.611
GOD HELP US.

38:34.613 --> 38:36.646
I DON'T KNOW.

38:36.648 --> 38:39.916
GIVEN THE CHOICE,
I PUT MY MONEY ON YOU.

38:39.918 --> 38:43.820
GOD'S THE ONE WHO
GOT US INTO THIS MESS.

38:47.759 --> 38:51.294
YOU KNOW, THERE'S ONE
POSSIBILITY YOU HAVEN'T
CONSIDERED ABOUT THOMAS.

38:51.296 --> 38:52.696
MAYBE HE'S NOT SICK.

38:52.698 --> 38:54.431
MAYBE HE'S HOME RIGHT
NOW HAVING DINNER

38:54.433 --> 38:58.301
AND WATCHING YOUTUBE,
LIKE EVERY OTHER
11-YEAR-OLD IN AMERICA.

38:58.303 --> 39:00.003
IT'S POSSIBLE.

39:01.807 --> 39:04.007
YEAH.

39:04.009 --> 39:05.675
IT'S POSSIBLE.

39:05.677 --> 39:09.012
HAVE YOU SEEN THE ONE
WHERE THE BULLDOG
PLAYS BASKETBALL?

39:11.550 --> 39:13.550
NO?

39:13.552 --> 39:16.219
Xander: AND HERE'S THE
OTHER THING, BABY GIRL.

39:16.221 --> 39:18.188
JUST BECAUSE YOU WANT
A LITTLE PERFECT ANGEL

39:18.190 --> 39:20.690
DOESN'T MEAN YOU CAN'T
TEAR 'EM UP ON THE
BASEBALL FIELD

39:20.692 --> 39:22.459
OR THE BASKETBALL COURT.

39:22.461 --> 39:24.327
WHAT IF SHE WANTS TO
PLAY HOCKEY?

39:24.329 --> 39:26.329
TOO COLD.
THAT'S TOO COLD.

39:26.331 --> 39:27.897
[KNOCK ON WINDOW]

39:30.736 --> 39:35.972
Chorus: ♪ BUT IF WE'RE STRONG
ENOUGH TO LET IT IN ♪

39:35.974 --> 39:38.208
♪ I-I-IN ♪

39:38.210 --> 39:40.076
♪ I-I-IN ♪

39:40.078 --> 39:44.714
♪ WE'RE STRONG ENOUGH
TO LET IT GO ♪

39:44.716 --> 39:46.716
♪ OH, OH, OH ♪

39:46.718 --> 39:49.552
♪ WHOA, OH,
LET IT ALL... ♪

39:49.554 --> 39:51.087
Jana: ROUGH DAY, HUH?

39:51.089 --> 39:54.090
LEO GREENE IS POND SCUM,
KING OF THE CLICK-BAIT.

39:54.092 --> 39:56.159
I MEAN, THE AMOUNT OF
LIVES THAT HE RISKED...

39:56.161 --> 39:58.995
YEAH, IT WORKED. HE'S GAINED
ALMOST A MILLION FOLLOWERS

39:58.997 --> 40:00.530
SINCE WEDNESDAY.

40:00.532 --> 40:02.932
WELL, I HATE
EVERY ONE TODAY,

40:02.934 --> 40:04.567
EXCEPT YOU.

40:04.569 --> 40:06.736
YOU, I--I DON'T HATE.

40:06.738 --> 40:08.905
YOU'RE THE ONLY ONE
AT THE MOMENT.

40:08.907 --> 40:11.841
YOU KNOW, JANA,
WHEN THIS IS OVER,

40:11.843 --> 40:15.378
I, UH--I DON'T WANT TO
SPEND ANOTHER NIGHT
AWAY FROM YOU.

40:15.380 --> 40:16.679
ME EITHER.

40:16.681 --> 40:18.448
NOT FOR A REALLY
LONG TIME.

40:18.450 --> 40:20.250
ME EITHER.

40:20.252 --> 40:23.353
FOR THE REST
OF MY LIFE.

40:23.355 --> 40:25.622
Chorus: ♪ BUT IF
WE'RE STRONG ENOUGH ♪

40:25.624 --> 40:27.123
ME EITHER, LEX.

40:27.125 --> 40:30.360
♪ TO LET IT IN,
I-I-IN ♪

40:30.362 --> 40:34.597
WELL, LET'S SEE IF THEY
HAVE AN EMOJI FOR THAT.

40:34.599 --> 40:36.099
HA HA HA!

40:36.101 --> 40:39.302
♪ TO LET IT GO, OH-- ♪
[CRACKLING]

40:41.706 --> 40:46.342
[PHONES BEEP;
COMPUTERS POWERING DOWN]

40:47.813 --> 40:49.979
[CLICKING KEYBOARD KEYS]

40:51.750 --> 40:53.983
[TELEPHONE RINGING]

41:01.726 --> 41:03.927
Dr. Victor: I JUST LOST
MY INTERNET CONNECTION.

41:03.929 --> 41:06.496
Sabine: YES. SO DID
EVERYONE IN THE CORDON.

41:06.498 --> 41:10.667
BUT DON'T WORRY. YOU'LL
HAVE A SECURE INTERNET
AND PHONE LINE TOMORROW,

41:10.669 --> 41:12.168
BUT ONLY YOU.

41:12.170 --> 41:14.471
THE REST OF THE AREA
WILL REMAIN DARK.

41:14.473 --> 41:16.005
[RECEIVER CLICKS]

41:18.143 --> 41:22.412
AFTER TODAY'S EVENTS,
THINGS WERE GETTING
AWAY FROM US.

41:22.414 --> 41:25.682
ANYWAY, LOSE CONTROL,
WE HAVE NO HOPE OF
GETTING IT BACK.

41:25.684 --> 41:27.917
THIS WAS FOR THE GOOD
OF EVERYONE.

41:27.919 --> 41:29.385
EVERYONE?

41:33.191 --> 41:36.526
YOU'RE LOOKING AT ME
LIKE THIS IS SOMEHOW
MY FAULT?

41:36.528 --> 41:39.829
I ASKED YOU TO STOP
LEO GREENE,
AND YOU DIDN'T.

41:39.831 --> 41:41.998
SO, IF YOU'RE LOOKING
FOR SOMEONE TO BLAME,

41:42.000 --> 41:46.469
MAJOR CARNAHAN,
BLAME YOURSELF.
